  <p>Containerized industrial centrifuges designed and manufactured by Dolphin Centrifuge have certain specifications depending on the size of the container, the scope of supply, and the type of centrifuges included in the module. A containerized decanter centrifuge fits within a 20&apos; or 40&apos; intermodal shipping container. A 40&apos; containerized decanter has the following specifications:</p>

