    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p>Dolphin Centrifuge has decades of experience designing and building containerized centrifuge systems. Whether you need a single-centrifuge diesel purification module or a complete multi-stage oil recovery plant, our engineering team can design a containerized solution for your specific application and environment.</p>

